{"tid":858793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿女情敵勾引未婚夫　跨性別者施襲囚20月","createTime":"2018-10-12T05:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T10:49:57.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4f51f418b16e5245a8306d63fd869d89158070f2","tid":858793,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181012/photo/bkn-20181012110738350-1012_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181012113349\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181012%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181012110738350-1012_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181012113349&h=01892519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">作女性化打扮的張澤釗今被判囚20個月。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n作女性化打扮、束長髮的無業男子，因不滿男朋友遭寄住家中的女性朋友「勾引」，他又遭女方批評「我唔覺你靚，我覺得我靚過你囉」，遂怒打女方的臉十多下，又剪她頭髮及拍照上載Facebook。其後無業男意外傷腿，他歸咎女方令他受傷，出手襲擊女方頭及雙膝等，又恐嚇會把女方2名女兒的手「斬落嚟」。28歲男被告張澤釗早前承認襲擊致造成身體傷害、有意圖傷人及刑事恐嚇共3罪，今日(12日)在區域法院被判囚20個月。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指，被告成長背景坎坷，父母自他幼年時已分開，由祖父母等照顧被告，得不到母親的照顧，對被告的成長及精神而言構成一定影響。而被告非兇狠或心地不好的人，被告免費讓事主在家中借住，只因兩人均有酗酒問題，繼而發生爭執推撞，引致後來的不幸事件，事主並無大礙，且事後仍續居其家。而辯方亦引述報告指被告有服食女性荷爾蒙藥。<br />\n<br />\n法官判刑時指控罪嚴重，被告因酗酒問題引致激烈反應，致傷害事主，幸未對事主造成永久傷害。而察閱被告的報告後，可見被告背景特殊，告誡被告在獄中好好反省，不要再酗酒，且其家人十分支持他，日後有問題應與家人商討解決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181012/bkn-20181012110738350-1012_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181012%2Fbkn-20181012110738350-1012_00822_001.html&d=651rJW1QGseCj5pgdxcXtmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=283fe419\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181012/bkn-20181012110738350-1012_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2d6e0b35d20cf899dbd1758f9b303048c2273807","tid":858793,"uid":19126,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:07:37.000Z","msg":"你老味個樣去拍西遊記連妝都唔洗化就拍得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0e30afacbae52131dec6fcc1c43ab29f8bb96f","tid":858793,"uid":511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:07:40.000Z","msg":"仲以為鬼妹嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae70b4b04ac34e88d0542a2fc071ee66f85085b0","tid":858793,"uid":144466,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:16:07.000Z","msg":"男監獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n急不及待想坐監了"},{"pid":"eac1ce4af250d9ac360bd25e1b036af5722e83ee","tid":858793,"uid":209956,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ae70b4b04ac34e88d0542a2fc071ee66f85085b0","tid":858793,"uid":144466,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:16:07.000Z","msg":"男監獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n急不及待想坐監了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/spP9mmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FspP9mmr.jpg&h=71580e89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c3bfa1982a1d2a70b611295c7e2fcb785876fa9","tid":858793,"uid":161990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死基佬"},{"pid":"f08626ea5ac355f650c98293aeb063939cd673e4","tid":858793,"uid":18040,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:31:34.000Z","msg":"又幾靚"},{"pid":"1282b129e79e79a01e5b691cce2601f4397bd5ba","tid":858793,"uid":50506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:35:15.000Z","msg":"只係佢女性打扮 但係又keep住食女性荷爾蒙藥？"},{"pid":"553c7a2dd00eccfedf7640e9af9da9fc79baa38f","tid":858793,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eac1ce4af250d9ac360bd25e1b036af5722e83e